							<tr>
								<td class="row2">
			<span class="gensmall"><b>File comment:</b> The title screen shown without sprites. There is garbage on the top line (hidden in NTSC). The pale blue square is intentional, hidden by a black sprite, I believe for a sprite 0 hit to switch tilesets.</span><br />
		
			<img src="./download/file.php?id=5607" alt="solstice_bad_title_bg.png" /><br />
