						<div class="postbody">tepples' RHDE did some of its text screens by combining 2 layers of text into a single block of CHR. Trades a palette slot to double the space available for 2-colour graphics. (Not related to Solstice, I don't think, but kind of in line with the idea you were just describing?)</div>

					
